stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> AsFound

    AsFound: As-found (before TW-GGEN-001)\nggen.toml does not reference ggen-verify-pack\nreceipt v2.equivalence: 6/8 classes Unknown

    AsFound --> TransitionOpen: ggen.toml edited to add\nggen-verify-pack reference\n(TW-GGEN-001 starts)

    TransitionOpen: Transition window open (TW-GGEN-001)\nEvery `ggen sync run` inspected:\ndiff v2.equivalence vs Unknown baseline\nwatch for spurious Divergent (wiring defect)\nmax lifetime 14 days

    TransitionOpen --> Inspecting: sync run
    Inspecting --> TransitionOpen: class regressed to Unknown\nOR spurious Divergent\n(Andon signal, fix and re-run)
    Inspecting --> GreenCycle: class correctly Equivalent/Divergent\n(real evidence, no wiring defect)

    GreenCycle --> TransitionOpen: fewer than 3 green\npre-commit cycles so far
    GreenCycle --> CICheck: 3rd green pre-commit cycle reached

    CICheck --> TransitionOpen: CI run not yet green
    CICheck --> Closed: pull_request CI green\n(3 green pre-commit + 1 green CI)

    Closed: Closed (success)\nWiring folded into permanent ggen.toml\nTW-GGEN-001 record marked Closed\n6/8 classes real going forward

    TransitionOpen --> RolledBack: 14-day max lifetime exceeded\nwithout 3 green + 1 green CI\nOR unfixable wiring defect

    RolledBack: Rolled back\nggen.toml reverted to pre-TW-GGEN-001 state\nreceipt returns to honest 6/8 Unknown\nitem #1 re-opened as deferred in decision-matrix.md

    Closed --> [*]
    RolledBack --> [*]

